OL,7,FThe son of caretaker Ian Coates, who
OL,8,Fwas killed in the Nottingham attacks,
OL,9,Fon the Care Quality Commission report
OL,10,Finto the level and quality of care
OL,11,Fgiven to Valdo Calocane.
OL,13,FThe families of the victims of Valdo
OL,14,FCalocane say services caring for him
OL,15,Fin the lead-up to the attacks "have
OL,16,Fblood on their hands".
OL,18,FIt comes after a mental health trust
OL,19,F"minimised or omitted" key details of
OL,20,Fthe serious risk he posed to others.
