OL,5,Comitted'
OL,7,FThe final part of a Care Quality
OL,8,FCommission (CQC) review into the care
OL,9,Fof Calocane by Nottinghamshire
OL,10,FHealthcare NHS Foundation Trust
OL,11,F(NHFT), found risk assessments played
OL,12,Fdown the fact he was refusing to take
OL,13,Fhis medication, and was having ongoing
OL,14,Fand persistent symptoms of psychosis.
OL,16,FIt also questions how well the trust
OL,17,Fengaged with Calocane's family, who
OL,18,Fraised concerns about his mental state.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/20
