OL,7,FThe victims' families said the CQC
OL,8,Freport "demonstrates gross, systematic
OL,9,Ffailures" and also claim they have had
OL,10,Fconfirmation that a public inquiry
OL,11,Finto the case will take place.
OL,13,FCalocane stabbed students 19-year old
OL,14,Fstudents Barnaby Webber and Grace
OL,15,FO'Malley-Kumar, as they returned from
OL,16,Fa night out in the early hours of June
OL,17,F13 last year.
OL,19,FHe then went on to kill 65-year old
OL,20,FIan Coates.
OL,26,@pD@HOUqD@IO]
