OL,7,FThe special review of mental health
OL,8,Fservices at NHFT was ordered by the-
OL,9,Fthen Health Secretary Victoria Atkins
OL,10,Fin January, after Calocane was
OL,11,Fsentenced to an indefinite hospital
OL,12,Forder.
OL,14,FThe CQC said Calocane's records make
OL,15,Fit "clear" that he was "acutely
OL,16,Funwell" throughout the two years he
OL,17,Fwas under the care of NHFT.
OL,26,@wD@DOUwD@JO]wD@XOUxD@GO]
