OL,7,FHe was psychotic and suffering from
OL,8,Fparanoid delusions, before eventually
OL,9,Fbeing diagnosed with paranoid
OL,10,Fschizophrenia in July 2020.
OL,12,FBetween May 2020 and February 2022,
OL,13,Feight risk assessments were completed
OL,14,Ffor Calocane by the trust, which the
OL,15,FCQC said appear to have been carried
OL,16,Fout for each of his admissions to
OL,17,Fhospital and updated at other times
OL,18,Fduring his care.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/20
