OL,7,FThe regulator said that while some
OL,8,Frisks were highlighted, other
OL,9,Fassessments "minimised or omitted key
OL,10,Fdetails". These include the fact
OL,11,FCalocane:
OL,13,F"The risk he presented to the public
OL,14,Fwas not managed well"
