OL,7,FChris Dzikiti, Interim Chief Inspector
OL,8,Fof healthcare at the CQC, said: "This
OL,9,Freview identifies points where poor
OL,10,Fdecision-making, omissions and errors
OL,11,Fof judgments contributed to a
OL,12,Fsituation where a patient with very
OL,13,Fserious mental health issues did not
OL,14,Freceive the support and follow-up he
OL,15,Fneeded.
OL,26,@pD@aOU
