OL,7,FInstead, he was treated under section
OL,8,F2 of the Act, which is usually for
OL,9,Fpatients who are not known to mental
OL,10,Fhealth services.
OL,12,F"We were failed by multiple
OL,13,Forganisations"
OL,15,FA statement from the families of
OL,16,FBarnaby Webber, Grace O'Malley-Kumar
OL,17,Fand Ian Coates, said: "This report
OL,18,Fdemonstrates gross, systematic
OL,19,Ffailures in the mental health trust in
OL,20,Ftheir dealings with Calocane, from
OL,21,Fbeginning to end.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@WOU
