OL,7,FThe CQC report also questioned how
OL,8,Fwell the Trust engaged with Calocane's
OL,9,Ffamily and how well his discharge was
OL,10,Fplanned.
OL,12,FIt comes after his mother Celeste and
OL,13,Fbrother Elias told the BBC's Panorama
OL,14,Fprogramme a psychiatrist warned
OL,15,FCalocane could "end up killing
OL,16,Fsomeone" three years before the
OL,17,Fattacks.
OL,26,@wD@POUxD@HO]
