OL,7,FThe handling of the Calocane case
OL,8,Fprompted outcry and led to numerous
OL,9,Finquiries into the public bodies
OL,10,Finvolved, including Nottinghamshire
OL,11,FPolice and Leicestershire Police."
OL,13,F"Blood on their hands"
OL,15,FThe victims' families said: "Along
OL,16,Fwith the Leicestershire and
OL,17,FNottinghamshire police forces, these
OL,18,Fdepartments and individual
OL,19,Fprofessionals have blood on their
OL,20,Fhands.
OL,26,@wD@]OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G17/20
