OL,5,Comitted'
OL,7,F"Alarmingly, there seems to be little
OL,8,For no accountability amongst the
OL,9,Fsenior management team within the
OL,10,Fmental health trust. We question how
OL,11,Fand why these people are still in
OL,12,Fposition."
OL,14,FA Nottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,15,FFoundation Trust spokesperson said:
OL,16,F"We acknowledge and accept the
OL,17,Fconclusions of this report and have
OL,18,Fsignificantly improved processes and
OL,19,Fstandards since the review was carried
OL,20,Fout."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@JO]xD@AOU|D@EO]
