OL,7,FMarjorie Wallace, Chief Executive of
OL,8,Fmental health charity Sane, said:
OL,9,F"This is the most damning indictment
OL,10,Fof the fact that psychiatric services
OL,11,Fare not in crisis but in complete
OL,12,Fbreakdown.
OL,14,F"The rights of patients override those
OL,15,Fof the families, carers and public.
OL,16,FHow can it be that a highly disturbed
OL,17,Fpatient with his history of sections
OL,18,Fand incidents of violence could choose
OL,19,Fnot to engage with services and
OL,20,Fdisappear into the community?
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOU
